- The integer matrix parameter `mat` must not be null.
- The integer parameter `threshold` is greater than or equal to 0 and is less than or equal to 100000.
- The integer result is the maximum side-length of a square with a sum less than or equal to the integer parameter `threshold`.
- If there is no square with a sum less than or equal to the integer parameter `threshold`, the integer result is equal to 0.
- The maximum side-length of the square is the length of the sides of the square.